 not needed, but the SSC model parameters\nrequire fine tuning. Both alternatives indicate that the sharp radio flare, if\nphysically connected to the preceding gamma-ray flares, can be reproduced only\nfor a very specific choice of parameters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Jan 2015 10:33:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 30 Jan 2015 10:47:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
