e formation\nand evolution of galaxies. Additionally, in the era of the James Webb Space\nTelescope this will become a flexible tool, applicable to any SFG up to z~3.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Jan 2015 15:24:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
